sources.title: Get That Man
sources.description: Title: Get That Man Summary: Life gets complicated for a taxi driver when it's discovered that he's the spitting image of the murdered heir to a fortune. Directed by: Spencer Gordon Bennet Actors: Wallace Ford, Finis Barton, E. Alyn Warren Production Company: Scott-Bennet Production Release Date: 11 July 1935 (USA) Aspect Ratio: 1.37 : 1 Life gets complicated for a taxi driver when it's discovered that he's the spitting image of the murdered heir to a fortune.
